data.description: Heavens a little closer in a house by the lake! That is exactly what you will find in this Lake Anna access home. Well-maintained doesn't begin to describe the level of care and attention to detail that has gone into this property, not to mention the tons of recent upgrades throughout. Sitting on just under an acre in a highly sought-after gated community, this 3BR/2BA home offers 2000 sq ft of living space. You will instantly be impressed upon entering the property with its freshly sealed, paved driveway and manicured landscaping. Stroll through the front door, through the inviting covered porch, and into the formal sitting area with a cozy wood-burning fireplace and beautiful new shiplap ceilings that span throughout the home. Next, you will enter the just-completed updated kitchen, complete with 42-inch cabinets, granite countertops with an inset sink, updated light fixtures, and stainless steel appliances. Right off the kitchen is an oversized family room to fit any family gathering, complete with a warm wood-burning stove and brand new carpeting. Enjoy your morning coffee or host family and friends in the all-seasons room with wall-to-wall windows and tile flooring. It is perfectly located right off the kitchen and leads to one of two rear decks. The spacious primary bedroom features an ensuite, a walk-in closet, new carpeting, and your own private access to the second rear deck, where you can soak away your trouble in your 6-person hot tub with privacy fencing. This home also has a detached garage with storage area and new garage door, a 16 x 20 shed with electric and wood stove, and a second 10 x 16 shed that also has electric. Never be left in the dark again; this home features a Generac generator with only five hours on it. There is a whole list of upgrades and recently done maintenance available at request, and high-speed internet is available. Most furniture can convey with acceptable offer. Enjoy true lake living with access to the public side of Lake Anna, and amenities such as a beach area, boat ramp, pavilion, gazebo, and weekend slips are available. You are conveniently located close to shopping, multiple dining options, a cidery, a taphouse, and a brewery that all host local events and entertainment. Lake Life is calling; you should answer!
